    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>五位奇女子,五段妙趣事,八荒行旧路,四海遇新人。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鬼谷八荒《五朵金花》内容包将为您带来五位不同于以往的独立定制形象的女修角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在八荒冒险的途中可以参与她们各自的故事、揭开她们各自的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她们也将于八荒活跃,对世界、人物产生各种影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外, 五名角色也将与玩家的历程中提供各种帮助,免于玩家为了各种所需疲于奔命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>胧之花</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras/2842cdc434c8d3e8e3e2ce87e85014c4.avif?t=1741762071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras_big/2842cdc434c8d3e8e3e2ce87e85014c4.avif?t=1741762071 width=800 height=336 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借用河图之力来到八荒的龙女，她为了保命和回家不得不四处探索寻找回归之法，但又因玩家的陪伴而难以割舍，可她最终必须做出抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>木之花</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras/6f643114b20ca1b6312265d0da1ed678.avif?t=1741762071\" width=616 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神祇制造的木偶之身，但木偶神识觉醒并尝试摆脱宿命，她希望成为一个人，而不是一具被人操纵的木偶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>墨之花</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras/d807f3bc912c7ce83b173017466933c4.avif?t=1741762071\" width=616 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受困书中的远古大能，她在玩家的协助下通过重重难关摆脱自己的困境，并于此过程中牵扯出一段八荒往事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>雪之花</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras/11a80611bd12404ddc3843593d4c100e.avif?t=1741762071\" width=616 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身怀玄冰之力动辄使身边陷入雪灾的女角色，她努力剔除自己的玄冰之力，希望能和喜欢的人在一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>帝之花</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326620/extras/aa897aa1bde945ba4d2ef38310c70187.avif?t=1741762071\" width=616 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寿命长久的女妖王，她以高人一等的视觉观察着世界万事，从而获得八荒的最终奥秘，但这一切将会让她付出惨痛代价。</p>",
